Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases where 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in successful payment cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time it takes from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' Cycle Time in cases leading to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER does not occur

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases followed by 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' without intermediate rejections
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases with direct approval flow (no rejections)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case
